beer.beer_description:
There's nothing better than opening your door to a couple of tiny merchants of diabetes in brown uniforms that bring delicious delights more addictive than heroin. 
And yes...it's totally acceptable to finish the entire box by yourself. And when the self loathing sets in and all you want to do is curl up in a cookie 
crumb filled ball of anxiety.....crack open this American Brown Ale....full of toasty and caramel goodness. 
It won't remove the anxiety and loathing...but it will wash down those cookies in the most delightful way
